@startuml MLECS_Sequence_Diagram

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #2C3E50
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #1565C0
skinparam sequenceGroupBackgroundColor #F5F5F5

title <size:16><b>MLECS Sequence Diagram</b></size>\n<size:11>Individual Credit Decision Process</size>

actor "Loan Officer" as LO #BBDEFB
participant "MLECS\nSystem" as SYS #E3F2FD
participant "SEP\nModule" as SEP #FFF8E1
participant "MLE\nModule" as MLE #E8F5E9
participant "ECS\nModule" as ECS #F3E5F5

== Credit Application Submission ==

LO -> SYS : Submit Credit Application\n(20 features)
activate SYS

SYS -> SYS : Preprocess Input\n(Encode, Scale)

== Ensemble Prediction ==

SYS -> SEP : Forward preprocessed features
activate SEP

SEP -> SEP : XGBoost predict → P₁ = 0.42
SEP -> SEP : LightGBM predict → P₂ = 0.35
SEP -> SEP : CatBoost predict → P₃ = 0.38
SEP -> SEP : Meta-Learner combine\nP(default|x) = σ(w₁·P₁ + w₂·P₂ + w₃·P₃ + b)

SEP --> SYS : P(default) = 0.38
deactivate SEP

== Multi-Level Explanation Generation ==

SYS -> MLE : Generate explanations\n(prediction + model access)
activate MLE

MLE -> MLE : Level 1: TreeSHAP global values
MLE -> MLE : Level 2: SHAP waterfall (local)
MLE -> MLE : Level 2: LIME surrogate (local)
MLE -> MLE : Level 3: DiCE counterfactuals\n(feasibility constraints applied)

== Consistency Evaluation ==

MLE -> ECS : SHAP values + LIME weights
activate ECS

ECS -> ECS : Compute Rank Correlation
ECS -> ECS : Compute Sign Agreement
ECS -> ECS : Compute Top-K Overlap

ECS --> MLE : ECS = 0.94 (consistent)
deactivate ECS

MLE --> SYS : Explanation Package\n(SHAP + LIME + Counterfactuals + ECS)
deactivate MLE

== Decision Delivery ==

SYS --> LO : **Decision:** APPROVED (P=0.38 < 0.5)\n**Top Risk Factors:** checking_status, duration, credit_amount\n**Recourse (if denied):** Reduce utilization, increase savings\n**Consistency:** ECS = 0.94 ✓
deactivate SYS

@enduml
